{
  "stem": "21319.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- but this-- this-- the bombing they did was around Auschwitz and Birkenau, around-- not in the camp, because they knew that there were people, innocent prisoners.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Innocent slaves.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they didn't bomb the camp itself, but they bombed around the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all the Nazis were hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You would see how they were running when we were to the windows, it's-- not till we live.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one more thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In November or December-- I think this was November-- a-- a-- the-- you know the-- the Sonderkommandos, when the people who used to burn and gas the people, every three month, they took them and they burn-- they gassed them and-- they took them on trains, they gassed them.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every three months, they collect new ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, one of the girls who were with me in the camp, her brother who came from Estonia was taken over to be a Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A young boy of 19 years or something was-- he was a big, tall young man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took them all on the-- in the trains, and they put the gas in and they gassed them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this last Sonderkommando decided, I'm not going to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're going to fight for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we remember like today there-- when they wanted to put him in the-- the-- all the big-- the big Nazis put them in the trains, they revolted.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They find grenades they stole from the-- knives, anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were fighting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were all killed, but they were killed like men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They weren't taken like sheep to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was the revolt from the Sonderkommando, the last one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was October or November.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
